Package gamelogic.terrains

Class TerrainModelErode

  • java.lang.Object
    • gamelogic.terrains.TerrainModelErode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TerrainModel, java.io.Serializable
    public class TerrainModelErode
extends java.lang.Object
implements TerrainModel
    Decreases the area of the terrain given in argument: a position will be included in the new terrain if it and all of its direct neighbors is included in the original terrain.
    Each position has 4 neighbors : up, down, left and right.
